ce:caption.ce:simple-para:
Amplitude and phase angle of THz electric field as a function of radiation frequency
f = ω / 2 π
for B-CQDs at different temperatures as indicated. The results for the phase angles coincide roughly. The inset shows the THz field transmitted through the B-CQDs in time-domain at a fixed temperature of 140 K. (A colour version of this figure can be viewed online.)
